{%- comment -%}
  Hamburger Menu Navigation Snippet
  -------------
  Renders the navigation menu content inside the hamburger drawer for mobile.
  Includes main menu items, mega menu submenus, and optional featured content.

  Parameters:
  - menu: The menu handle to use for navigation items (defaults to 'main-menu')
  - blocks: Theme section blocks containing mega menu configurations
      Each block can define:
      - Parent link title to match with menu item
      - Up to 3 submenus with titles
      - Featured content with image, title and URL
{%- endcomment -%}
